HEADWORD: code-breaking
<hw>code"-break`ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A process of
discovering the content of an encoded message or the nature of a
<er>code</er>{5}. The method used may be surreptitious, or may use
sophisticated mathematical and computational techniques to discover the
code.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

